text: Sikri may refer to: * Sikri, Ballabhgarh, a village in Ballabhgarh tehsil of Faridabad district in Haryana, India * Sikri, St. Kabir Nagar, a village in Uttar Pradesh, India * Sikri, Phagwara, a village in Punjab, India *Fatehpur Sikri, a town in the Agra District of Uttar Pradesh, India.
title: Sikri
